FOLDER.NAME: EDWTD_POS
FOLDER.DESCRIPTION: This is for EDW TeraData Sales Orders and POS Track PM:vinit verma

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT WIP.TRANS_ID, WIP.ID, WIP.BOOKING_FLAG, NVL(WIP.SERVICE_TYPE,'UNKNOWN'), WIP.ACTIVE_FLAG, WIP.CREATED_DATE, WIP.CREATED_BY, WIP.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, WIP.LAST_UPDATED_BY, NVL(WIP. QUOTE_NUMBER,'UNKNOWN'), NVL(WIP. CONTRACT_NUMBER,'UNKNOWN'), NVL(WIP. QUOTE_LINE_ID,-999), /* NVL(WIP. ORDER_LINE_ID,-9999),*/ CASE WHEN WIP.ORDER_LINE_ID = -6666 THEN -9999 ELSE NVL(WIP.ORDER_LINE_ID,-9999) END AS ORDER_LINE_ID, NVL(MATCH_TYPE, 'UNKNOWN'), NVL(CAST(ORDER_HEADER_ID AS VARCHAR2(150)),'-999') , NVL(CAST(QUOTE_HEADER_ID AS VARCHAR2(150)),'-9999') , NVL(REVENUE_SOURCE_CODE, 'U' ), NVL(WIP.CONFIDENCE_FLAG, 'N') , WIP.PO_EXISTS , WIP.PO_DISTI_EXISTS , WIP.PO_PID_EXISTS , WIP.QUOTE_EXISTS , WIP.QUOTE_DISTI_EXISTS , WIP.QUOTE_PID_EXISTS , WIP.MULTIPLE_SALES_MOTION, WIP.MULTIPLE_MATCH, WIP.APPROVED_ERP_LINKAGE, WIP.ORDER_IDENTIFIER FROM XXDISTIPUB.WIPS_SER_POS_DTLS_PUB WIP WHERE WIP.LAST_UPDATED_DATE > TO_DATE('$$LastExtractDate','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')
